    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Recently I have heard and read about reports of disc-shaped aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "or whatever they are, in our western regions. They reminded me of a nearly",
      "status": "image_matched"
