      "text": "I feel this may be of international scope.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "My buddy and I went on pass to see a friend of his. One evening the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
