      "text": "looking object in the sky from eight to ten miles to our front and approx-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "imately 5,000 feet high.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "I immediatly stopped the jeep for a better look. The object rapidly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "came toward us, descending slowly. About a mile away it stopped it's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "horizontal motion but continued a slow oscillating descent, similar to a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "descending parachute. Then suddenly it dropped in a spiral motion.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Immediatly I drove over to where it had dropped. It took almost five",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "minutes to reach the place but we saw nothing. After ten minutes of cruis-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "ing around the area it became too dark to see so we went back to town.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "because",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "I am not sure my companions saw this, it happened so quickly it could",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "easily have been missed, but I described what I had seen so vividly that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "they were as excited as I was. My first impression was that it was a cloud",
